ws/music/red-velvets-irene-to-make-solo-debut-with-like-a-flower-3809169">Red Velvet 成员 Irene 将以单曲《Like A Flower》</a>首次亮相<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a> 。</p> ;
