gh-hole-on-stage-in-melbourne-3802687">在墨尔本经历了类似的事件</a>。罗德里戈（Rodrigo）上个月在罗德·拉弗竞技场（Rod Laver Arena）参加“胆量”世界巡回演出时，在舞台上的一个洞里摔倒了，然后迅速弹出并打趣：“哦，天哪，这很有趣！我没事！哇。有时，舞台上只有一个洞。没关系！好吧，我在哪里？”</p><p>明年，Coldplay将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-uk-tour-stadium-london-wembley-hull-music-venue-trust-tickets-3794308">返回英国参加伦敦和赫尔的表演</a>之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-music-of-the-spheres-2025-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3800743">，将他们的“球形音乐”世界巡回演出前往北美</a>。他们将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-two-extra-wembley-stadium-shows-due-to-phenomenal-demand-buy-tickets-3797381">在首都温布利体育场（Wembley Stadium）进行历史悠久的10晚跑步</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-to-break-taylor-swift-and-take-thats-wembley-stadium-record-with-huge-10-night-run-3797432#:~:text=The%20run%20was%20originally%20meant,nights%20in%20the%20English%20capital.">击败了泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）创下的以前的场地纪录并接受</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800752" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800752" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800752" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Coldplay的Chris Martin在2023年表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Coldplay@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800752" class="wp-caption-text"> Coldplay的Chris Martin在2023年演出（Sergione Infuso/Corbis通过ABA的Getty Images拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p> Coldplay最近在10月初发行了他们的第10张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/coldplay-moon-music-review-3798469">“ Moon Music”</a> 。此后，它已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplays-moon-music-is-the-fastest-selling-album-by-a-uk-act-this-year-so-far-3800697">成为迄今为止在2024年英国法案中最快的销售记录</a>，自从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Adele">阿黛尔（Adele</a> ）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/adele-30-album-review-dependable-pop-titan-finally-mixes-things-up-3096613">“ 30”</a>以来，英国在英国官方专辑排行榜上获得了最大的一周。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="625" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-chris-martin-playlist-fontaines-d-c-peggy-gou-3798454"><b>独家：查看Coldplay的Chris Martin的NME播放列表</b></a></li></ul><p>在唱片发行之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/coldplay-chris-martin-exclusive-nme-interview-moon-music-3798496">马丁在他的专辑唯一书面采访中与<i>NME</i>进行了交谈</a>。广泛的谈话使主持人揭示了启发唱片的主题以及乐队如何撰写新音乐的结尾。</p><p>至于Coldplay是否<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-only-making-three-more-studio-albums-3071632">仍计划在12张专辑后总结他们的录制目录</a>，Martin告诉<i>NME</i> ：“ 12张专辑非常真实，这是一种很好的感觉。这并不意味着我们不会参观或完成一些汇编的内容，耗车等。这仅意味着讲述了主要故事。那就是真正正确的。仅仅知道发生这种情况就会增强我们现在正在进行的所有工作。” </p><figure id="attachment_3795325" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3795325" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3795325" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Chris-Martin-of-Coldplay.-CREDIT_-Monica-Schipper_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3795325" class="wp-caption-text"> Coldplay的Chris Martin。图片来源：莫妮卡·史珀（Monica Schipper）/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>马丁在其他地方说，这个截止日期<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-chris-martin-band-end-final-albums-3798614">导致成员在创造性的方法中具有“更多的饥饿”</a> ，并决心确保他们不会“稀释”自己发布的任何东西。他向粉丝保证，到他们的第12张专辑完成时，就Coldplay的故事而言，“一切都会有意义”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/coldplay-chris-martin-exclusive-nme-interview-moon-music-3798496">阅读<i>NME</i>在此处对Martin的独家采访</a>，他还谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a> ，Coldplay <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/coldplay-glastonbury-2024-live-review-photos-setlist-3770486">在Glastonbury 2024的历史制作</a>和乐队的誓言等人的历史制作，以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-uk-tour-stadium-london-wembley-hull-music-venue-trust-tickets-3794308">帮助支持整个英国的基层场地</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplays-chris-martin-falls-through-trap-door-while-performing-in-melbourne-3809137">Coldplay的克里斯·马丁（Chris Martin）在墨尔本演出时跌落在陷阱门上，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
